[h4 id=Nvr_2 
	" NVR
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"The default NVR file used is 
	[code 
		"pb570.nvr
	]code
	" (md5: 
	[code 
		"9228bf13f3fe46351b1885e073558b67
	]code
	"). It can be found in the folder you installed PCem in under 
	[code 
		"/nvr/default/pb570.nvr
	]code
	". To be completely sure your NVR file starts off clean, take this file, copy it to 
	[code 
		"~/.pcem/nvr/
	]code
	" and name it after your config file (e.g. if your config is named early90s, name it 
	[code 
		"early90s.pb570.nvr
	]code
	".) If there is already a file named this, delete it and replace it.
	$LF
]div
